top%3D1&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5zsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=ee27f0bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5zsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=10793fc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"6d8f59f8f291e3779c96ae485c21fde92878283c","tid":1679280,"uid":29560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"又玩抹黑 block<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8ed20d88bf174a1cd2a0f4c1a644d869e8be86","tid":1679280,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:27:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>主線速遞</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期六 11 &middot; 2 </span><br />\n求援國際 堅守自治</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 維園流水式集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678270/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678270/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">星期六 11 &middot; 9 </span><br />\n柏林圍牆倒塌30周年集會</strong></span><br />\n- 19:30 中環愛丁堡廣場<br /